metadata.name: MAD Angel #1
metadata.description:
Here's to the thinkers, the builders, the creatives, the visionaries, the social connectors. Here's to the ones who care about the environment, about education, healthcare, equality, access, and more. Here's to a collective of individuals who are building a future that's more sustainable. 
 
Maybe only the ones crazy enough can change the world, but anyone can Make A Difference #MAD.
